algorithms.imageProcessing

Class DoubleLinkedCircularList

  • java.lang.Object
    • algorithms.imageProcessing.DoubleLinkedCircularList

  • public class DoubleLinkedCircularList
extends java.lang.Object
    a doubly linked list with a sentinel in between the last and first item. created specifically to hold Fibonacci Heap nodes. 
     Runtime complexity:
 insert is O(1)
 search is O(N)
 delete if given node is O(1), else O(N)
    Author:
    nichole
